<text><body>
<lb n="0523c15"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0523c16"/>
<lb n="0523c17"/><head type="no">No. 1122</head>
<lb n="0523c18"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0523001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】明本，【甲】三十帖策子第十九</note>金剛頂瑜伽他化自在天理趣會
<lb n="0523c19"/>普賢修行念誦儀<note n="0523002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軌＋（一卷）【甲】</note><app n="0523002"><lem>軌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">軌一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0523c20"/>
<lb n="0523c21"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0523003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔唐〕－【甲】</note><app n="0523003"><lem>唐</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>特進試鴻臚卿<note n="0523004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大興善寺）＋三【甲】</note><app n="0523004"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺三</rdg></app>藏沙門
<lb n="0523c22"/>大廣<note n="0523005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔智〕－【甲】</note><app n="0523005"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0523c23"/><div1 type="jing"><lg><l>我以淨三業</l><l>為利諸眾生</l>
<lb n="0523c24"/><l>令得三身故</l><l>歸命禮三寶</l>
<lb n="0523c25"/><l>金剛身語意</l><l>遍滿生死中</l>
<lb n="0523c26"/><l>祕密金剛界</l><l>大悲依護者</l>
<lb n="0523c27"/><l>雄猛阿&CB00434;鞞</l><l>最勝寶生尊</l>
<lb n="0523c28"/><l>大悲阿彌陀</l><l>成就不空業</l>
<lb n="0523c29"/><l>此諸無上尊</l><l>我皆稽首禮</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0524a" n="0524a"/>
<lb n="0524a01"/><l>及薩埵金剛</l><l>降伏於一切</l>
<lb n="0524a02"/><l>勝上虛空藏</l><l>能授諸灌頂</l>
<lb n="0524a03"/><l>救世觀自在</l><l>顯三昧瑜伽</l>
<lb n="0524a04"/><l>巧毘首羯磨</l><l>善作密方便</l>
<lb n="0524a05"/><l>如上諸聖尊</l><l>我皆稽首禮</l>
<lb n="0524a06"/><l>脩行此法者</l><l>常住本尊觀</l>
<lb n="0524a07"/><l>行步踐蓮華</l><l>至於精室門</l>
<lb n="0524a08"/><l>彈指三稱吽</l><l>右目置麼字</l>
<lb n="0524a09"/><l>左目置吒字</l><l>右日左成月</l>
<lb n="0524a10"/><l>流散金剛光</l><l>入門而顧視</l>
<lb n="0524a11"/><l>諸魔咸消散</l><l>以左金剛拳</l>
<lb n="0524a12"/><l>當心&CB00594;頭指</l><l>右手亦復然</l>
<lb n="0524a13"/><l>頂上三左旋</l><l>指空及下界</l>
<lb n="0524a14"/><l>次復右旋轉</l><l>皆誦吽字明</l>
<lb n="0524a15"/><l>次思佛常住</l><l>置禮三寶已</l>
<lb n="0524a16"/><l>方誦清淨明</l><l>二手未敷蓮</l>
<lb n="0524a17"/><l>加心額喉頂</l></lg>
<lb n="0524a18"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0524001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝娑【甲】</note><app n="0524001"><lem>莎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">娑</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;&CB02122;鐸薩&CB00085;達莫<note place="inline">引</note>莎&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0524a19"/>婆<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;戍度憾</p>
<lb n="0524a20"/><lg><l>此明密義云</l><l>諸法自性淨</l>
<lb n="0524a21"/><l>我亦自性淨</l><l>由是加持故</l>
<lb n="0524a22"/><l>自他獲無垢</l><l>便於自心中</l>
<lb n="0524a23"/><l>觀<note n="0524002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">性＝吽【甲】</note><app n="0524002"><lem>性</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">吽</rdg></app>成金剛</l><l>三業已轉依</l>
<lb n="0524a24"/><l>成三<note n="0524003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祕密＝密祕【甲】</note><app n="0524003"><lem>祕密</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">密祕</rdg></app>門</l><l>次作發悟契</l>
<lb n="0524a25"/><l>二拳檀慧鉤</l><l>進力側相<note n="0524004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【甲】＊</note><app n="0524004"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">跓</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0524a26"/><l><note n="0524005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝三【甲】＊</note><app n="0524005"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>舉如鉤勢</l><l>誦此祕密言</l></lg>
<lb n="0524a27"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日&CB00080;<note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟吒<note n="0524006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0524006"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0524a28"/><lg><l>由此真語印加持</l><l>諸佛不貪寂靜味</l>
<lb n="0524a29"/><l>悉從定起赴集會</l><l>觀察行人同攝<note n="0524007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【甲】</note><app n="0524007"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app></l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0524b" n="0524b"/>
<lb n="0524b01"/><l>次結金剛持大印</l><l>檀慧禪智反相叉</l>
<lb n="0524b02"/><l><note n="0524008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝又【甲】＊</note><app n="0524008"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">又</rdg></app>膝著地置頂上</l><l>想身遍滿塵剎海</l>
<lb n="0524b03"/><l>敬禮一一如來足</l></lg>　　<p place="inline">真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524b04"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0524009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝一&CB00085;一【甲】</note><app n="0524009"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一&CB00085;一</rdg></app>日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>忽<note place="inline">微<note n="0524010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言切＝一反【甲】</note><app n="0524010"><lem>言切</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一反</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0524b05"/><lg><l>由此金剛持印故</l><l>一切正覺皆隨順</l>
<lb n="0524b06"/><l>為欲奉事諸如來</l><l>捨身奉獻阿&CB00434;佛</l>
<lb n="0524b07"/><l>金剛合掌舒頂上</l><l>全身委地以心禮</l></lg>
<lb n="0524b08"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524b09"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">引</note>孽跢<note place="inline">引</note>布儒<note place="inline">引</note>波娑他<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0524005"><lem>二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三</rdg></app>合</note>娜
<lb n="0524b10"/>夜怛麼<note place="inline">二合引</note>南<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">引</note>哩夜<note place="inline">二合下同</note>多夜弭薩&CB00085;怛
<lb n="0524b11"/>他<note place="inline">引</note>孽多<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵<note place="inline">引</note>地瑟&CB00062;<note place="inline">二合下同</note>莎
<lb n="0524b12"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合下同</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">引</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0524b13"/><lg><l>由<note n="0524011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝以【甲】＊</note><app n="0524011"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>真言身印故</l><l>即得圓滿菩提心</l>
<lb n="0524b14"/><l>次應敬禮寶生尊</l><l>為奉灌頂承事故</l>
<lb n="0524b15"/><l>金剛合掌下當心</l><l>以額著地而奉獻</l></lg>
<lb n="0524b16"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524b17"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">引</note>孽多布惹毘曬迦夜怛麼<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0524b18"/>南&CB00135;哩夜多夜弭薩&CB00085;怛他孽多&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0524b19"/>囉怛娜<note place="inline">二合引</note>毘詵左&CB00805;怛<note n="0524012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洛＝&CB02255;【甲】</note><app n="0524012"><lem>洛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB02255;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0524b20"/><lg><l>由此捨身供養故</l><l>即獲灌頂法王位</l>
<lb n="0524b21"/><l>為欲求請轉法輪</l><l>捨身供養無量壽</l>
<lb n="0524b22"/><l>金剛合掌置頂上</l><l>以口著地奉其身</l></lg>
<lb n="0524b23"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524b24"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">引</note>孽<note n="0524013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哆＝跢【甲】</note><app n="0524013"><lem>哆</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">跢</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>布惹&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺多娜
<lb n="0524b25"/><note place="inline">引</note>夜怛麼南&CB00135;哩夜多夜弭薩&CB00085;怛他孽多&CB00085;
<lb n="0524b26"/>日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達磨&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺多也<note n="0524014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00805;＝&CB14287;【甲】</note><app n="0524014"><lem>&CB00805;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB14287;</rdg></app>紇哩</p>
<lb n="0524b27"/><lg><l>由<app type="＊" source="0524011"><lem>此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以</rdg></app>真言求請故</l><l>即獲轉妙法輪智</l>
<lb n="0524b28"/><note n="0524015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（次應…故）十四字＝（為欲成佛事業故次應禮事不空尊）十四字【甲】</note><app n="0524015" word-count="14"><lem><l>次應敬禮不空王</l><l>為求供養羯磨故</l></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">為欲成佛事業故次應禮事不空尊</rdg></app>
<lb n="0524b29"/><l>金剛合掌當心上</l><l>以頂著地而求請</l></lg>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0524c" n="0524c"/>
<lb n="0524c01"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524c02"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">引</note>孽多<note place="inline">引</note>布惹羯磨抳阿<note place="inline">引</note>怛<note n="0524016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝麼【甲】＊</note><app n="0524016"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>
<lb n="0524c03"/>南&CB00135;哩夜多夜弭薩&CB00085;怛他孽多<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0524c04"/>合</note>羯磨句嚕&CB00805;惡</p>
<lb n="0524c05"/><lg><l>由是獻身<note n="0524017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誠＝成【甲】</note><app n="0524017"><lem>誠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>請故</l><l>便能示現種種身</l>
<lb n="0524c06"/><l>次想己身佛海前</l><l>懺悔隨<note n="0524018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝喜【甲】</note><app n="0524018"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">喜</rdg></app>勸請向</l>
<lb n="0524c07"/><l>如是並依略瑜伽</l><l>即入本尊三昧耶</l>
<lb n="0524c08"/><l><note n="0524019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跏坐＝結跏【甲】</note><app n="0524019"><lem>跏坐</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">結跏</rdg></app>端身入正受</l><l>四無量心盡法界</l>
<lb n="0524c09"/><l>修習運用如法教</l></lg>
<lb n="0524c10"/><p>大慈真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524c11"/><p type="dharani">唵麼訶昧怛&CB00942;<note place="inline">二合</note>娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉</p>
<lb n="0524c12"/><lg><l>誦是真言時</l><l>演心遍三界</l>
<lb n="0524c13"/><l>普施眾生樂</l></lg>
<lb n="0524c14"/><p>大悲真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524c15"/><p type="dharani">唵麼訶迦嚕拏娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉</p>
<lb n="0524c16"/><lg><l>誦是真言時</l><l>心遍眾生界</l>
<lb n="0524c17"/><l>普門為拯濟</l></lg>
<lb n="0524c18"/><p>大喜真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524c19"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;&CB02122;馱&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>謨娜娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉</p>
<lb n="0524c20"/><lg><l>隨類拯救已</l><l>以此明加持</l>
<lb n="0524c21"/><l>一切有情類</l><l>咸授與菩提</l>
<lb n="0524c22"/><l>如是利樂已</l><l>方歸法界性</l></lg>
<lb n="0524c23"/><p>大捨真言曰</p>
<lb n="0524c24"/><p type="dharani">唵麼護閉叉娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉</p>
<lb n="0524c25"/><lg><l>念此真言時</l><l>心住於平等</l>
<lb n="0524c26"/><l>不見有自他</l><l>唯此一性相</l>
<lb n="0524c27"/><l>即是普賢性</l><l>大菩提之心</l></lg>
<lb n="0524c28"/><p>次應二手旋舞。作金剛合掌印。十度初分相
<lb n="0524c29"/>交是也真言曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0525a" n="0525a"/>
<lb n="0525a01"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日&CB01836;<note place="inline">二合引</note>惹里</p>
<lb n="0525a02"/><p>以此印便堅固縛。名勝上金剛縛。一切契皆
<lb n="0525a03"/>從此生真言曰</p>
