<lb n="0525a15"/><lg><l>次當開心門</l><l>觀於二乳上</l>
<lb n="0525a16"/><l><app type="＊" source="0524008"><lem>右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">又</rdg></app>怛囉左吒</l><l>三掣金剛縛</l>
<lb n="0525a17"/><l>當心如啟扇</l></lg>　　<p place="inline">真言曰</p>
<lb n="0525a18"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱怛囉<note n="0525002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0525002"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吒<note place="inline">半<note n="0525003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＋（三合）【甲】</note><app n="0525003"><lem>音</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">音三合</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0525a19"/><lg><l>觀前一肘間</l><l>惡字素光色</l>
<lb n="0525a20"/><l>禪智入月掌</l><l>以進力二度</l>
<lb n="0525a21"/><l>捻字安心內</l></lg>　　<p place="inline">真言曰</p>
<lb n="0525a22"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吠舍惡</p>
<lb n="0525a23"/><lg><l>以前拳印明</l><l>封閉心殿門</l>
<lb n="0525a24"/><l>密<note n="0525004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">闔＝合【甲】</note><app n="0525004"><lem>闔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">合</rdg></app>心門已</l>
<lb n="0525a25"/><l>分二當心前</l><l>稱吽舉<note n="0525005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝左【甲】</note><app n="0525005"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">左</rdg></app>噓</l>
<lb n="0525a26"/><l>次吽舉同左</l><l>三吽相鉤結</l>
