<lb n="0525b13"/><note place="inline">二合二</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>馱囉<note place="inline">三</note>薩帝娜&CB00062;<note place="inline">入<note n="0525011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聲〕－【甲】</note><app n="0525011"><lem>聲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note></p>
