<lb n="0525b19"/>佉&CB00085;日&CB00771;<note place="inline">二合</note>莎馱也薩&CB00085;薩底<note n="0525013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吠＝&CB05459;【甲】＊</note><app n="0525013"><lem>吠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB05459;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>瓢<note place="inline">毘藥
<lb n="0525b20"/><note n="0525014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切＝反【甲】</note><app n="0525014"><lem>切</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app></note>惹吽&CB00805;穀</p>
