<lb n="0525b29"/><lg><l>由<note n="0525017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝此【甲】＊</note><app n="0525017"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>三密門</l><l>盡集自他業</l>
