<lb n="0525c27"/><lg><l>由此法加持</l><l>三毒咸消<note n="0525026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">終＝殄【甲】</note><app n="0525026"><lem>終</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">殄</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0525c28"/><l>自心大菩提</l><l>當時便成就</l></lg>
<lb n="0525c29"/><lg><l>次入妙觀察智定</l><l>縛印仰置跏趺上</l>
