<lb n="0526a01"/><l>進力相背&CB00594;頭合</l><l>禪智相<app type="＊" source="0524004"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg></app>押進力</l>
<lb n="0526a02"/><l>此名觀自在王印</l><l>端身正坐身無動</l>
<lb n="0526a03"/><l>舌<app type="＊" source="0524004"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg></app>上&CB00171;唇齒合</l><l>心住大空無分別</l>
<lb n="0526a04"/><l>諸佛滿空來警悟</l><l>告言汝證一道淨</l>
<lb n="0526a05"/><l>未證金剛<note n="0526001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瑜＝踰【甲】＊</note><app n="0526001"><lem>瑜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">踰</rdg></app>伽定</l><l>便於定中禮佛足</l></lg>
<lb n="0526a06"/><p>餘文廣依<app type="＊" source="0526001"><lem>瑜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">踰</rdg></app>伽經所說。誦是真言。前<note n="0526002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＋（說）【甲】</note><app n="0526002"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">所說</rdg></app>內
<lb n="0526a07"/>心惡字。從字出無量赤光。右旋成日真言曰</p>
