<lb n="0526b03"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛娜<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0526b04"/><p>次後法曰</p>
<lb n="0526b05"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達磨</p>
<lb n="0526b06"/><p>次左業曰</p>
<lb n="0526b07"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>羯磨</p>
<lb n="0526b08"/><p>密印。本縛忍願如刀。進力附是也。由是加持
<lb n="0526b09"/>已。五如來冠在其頂。便分為二拳。至頂後進
<lb n="0526b10"/>力三相繞。下散垂繒勢。是名鬘灌頂。則為已
<lb n="0526b11"/>繫離垢繒真言曰</p>
<lb n="0526b12"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="＊" source="0524016"><lem>磨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">麼</rdg></app>&CB00619;阿毘詵左&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0526b13"/><p>便以二<note n="0526005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔手〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0526005"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>為拳。舒進力。於進指面想唵<note n="0526006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔字〕－【甲】</note><app n="0526006"><lem>字</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0526b14"/>力度面置砧字。綠色白光。如抽藕絲。為鉀縚
<lb n="0526b15"/>索。從心三繞背後亦然。次臍及腰兩膝又臍
<lb n="0526b16"/>腰心背咽喉頸後額前頂後。皆三繞下散。如
<lb n="0526b17"/>垂天衣。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0526b18"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>迦&CB00085;際&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>句&CB00080;&CB00085;日
<lb n="0526b19"/><note n="0526007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">邏＝囉【甲】＊</note><app n="0526007"><lem>邏</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾</p>
<lb n="0526b20"/><p>作是加持。則為已被三世如來大誓莊嚴慈
<lb n="0526b21"/>悲甲冑。一切天魔不能為障。則能摧敗一切
<lb n="0526b22"/>魔軍。作諸佛事利樂有情。為悅眾聖速獲成
<lb n="0526b23"/>就。以二羽三相拍。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0526b24"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;史也<note place="inline">二合</note>穀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0526b25"/><lg><l>由以拍印加持故</l><l>一切眾聖皆歡喜</l>
<lb n="0526b26"/><l>次復前觀本尊心</l><l>變為本尊妙身相</l>
<lb n="0526b27"/><l>如前自觀今亦然</l><l>為顯法智體無二</l>
<lb n="0526b28"/><l>前觀五相所成就</l><l>所謂自性之法身</l>
<lb n="0526b29"/><l>今所觀者是智身</l><l>住是三麼地祕門</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0526c" n="0526c"/>
<lb n="0526c01"/><l>本縛禪智入於月</l></lg>　　<p place="inline">真言曰</p>
<lb n="0526c02"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵惡<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵&CB00135;
<lb n="0526c03"/>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>捨也<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0526c04"/><lg><l>由是加持故</l><l>尊身則明顯</l>
<lb n="0526c05"/><l>便召入自身</l><l>次於所居處</l>
<lb n="0526c06"/><l>復觀阿字門</l><l>成妙高山王</l>
<lb n="0526c07"/><l>上有寶樓閣</l><l>於是宮殿內</l>
<lb n="0526c08"/><l>復安本尊身</l><l>眷屬皆圍繞</l>
<lb n="0526c09"/><l>種種供養具</l><l>法界所有物</l>
<lb n="0526c10"/><l>皆悉滿其中</l><l>作是觀念時</l>
<lb n="0526c11"/><l>誦此真言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0526c12"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00344;&CB00344;娜三婆&CB00085;&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0526008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穀＋（引）細註【甲】</note><app n="0526008"><lem>穀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">穀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0526c13"/><lg><l>由斯真言威德故</l><l>一切供具皆充滿</l>
<lb n="0526c14"/><l>所欲咸從空庫生</l><l>為欲奉事本尊故</l>
<lb n="0526c15"/><l>當<note n="0526009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">往＝住【甲】</note><app n="0526009"><lem>往</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>成所作智定</l><l>如是觀念加持已</l></lg>
<lb n="0526c16"/><p>當以不空王召集眾聖</p>
<lb n="0526c17"/><lg><l>定慧二羽金剛拳</l><l>交臂抱胸屈進力</l>
<lb n="0526c18"/><l>彈指發聲遍世界</l><l>諦觀佛海普雲集</l></lg>
<lb n="0526c19"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0526c20"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>三麼惹<note n="0526010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝惹【甲】</note><app n="0526010"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惹</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0526c21"/><lg><l>由以真言密印故</l><l>本尊及與眾聖等</l>
<lb n="0526c22"/><l>降臨<note n="0526011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03203;＝側【甲】</note><app n="0526011"><lem>&CB03203;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">側</rdg></app>塞虛空中</l><l>次住平等性智定</l>
<lb n="0526c23"/><l>捧持閼伽眾香水</l><l>灌沐眾聖無垢身</l>
<lb n="0526c24"/><l>應以金剛合掌印</l><l>加持香水誦真言</l></lg>
<lb n="0526c25"/><p type="dharani">唵跛囉麼速佉捨也莎羅里多娜麼帶囉娜麼
<lb n="0526c26"/>弭<note n="0526012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帶＝薄【甲】</note><app n="0526012"><lem>帶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">薄</rdg></app>&CB00344;挽擔若吽&CB00805;穀<note place="inline">引</note>呬<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底縒
<lb n="0526c27"/>俱蘇麼惹稜娜託</p>
<lb n="0526c28"/><p>便以色召聖者。入殿內<note n="0526013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝置【甲】</note><app n="0526013"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">置</rdg></app>身。以三世印。進
<lb n="0526c29"/>召如鉤真言曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0527a" n="0527a"/>
<lb n="0527a01"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>嚕閉惹</p>
<lb n="0527a02"/><p>召已。又用聲引入智同一。以進力相<app type="＊" source="0524004"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg></app>如索
<lb n="0527a03"/>是也。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0527a04"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>攝泥吽</p>
<lb n="0527a05"/><p>同一密合已。復以香止住。以進力度鉤結如
<lb n="0527a06"/>連鎖是也。真言曰</p><p type="dharani" place="inline">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>巘第&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0527a07"/><p>固縛已。又用味悅喜。以進力面相合是也。真
<lb n="0527a08"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0527a09"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0527001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝&CB00256;引【甲】</note><app n="0527001"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00256;引</rdg></app>細<note place="inline">引</note>穀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0527a10"/><p>應以語言而為歌詠。次結本尊印及真言。又
<lb n="0527a11"/>以二<app type="＊" source="0526005"><lem>手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>如射。名曰意生曰</p><p type="dharani" place="inline">唵麼努<note place="inline">引</note>娜婆
<lb n="0527a12"/><note place="inline">二合下同</note>&CB00085;&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>若</p>
<lb n="0527a13"/><p>又以二交臂如抱。慧覆定。名觸曰</p>
<lb n="0527a14"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>計里枳羅吽</p>
<lb n="0527a15"/><p>又以慧肘。極安定禪進。名愛縛曰</p>
<lb n="0527a16"/><p type="dharani">唵塞泥賀縛日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0527a17"/><p>又以二腰側。名意氣曰</p>
<lb n="0527a18"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>孽<note n="0527002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0527002"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>穀</p>
<lb n="0527a19"/><p>又以二如前耎射。名意生女曰</p>
<lb n="0527a20"/><p type="dharani">唵麼努娜婆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>呬<note place="inline"><note n="0527003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（入）【甲】</note><app n="0527003"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">引入</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0527a21"/><p>又如前觸。名適悅女曰</p>
<lb n="0527a22"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>計里<note n="0527004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枳＝&CB00242;【甲】</note><app n="0527004"><lem>枳</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00242;</rdg></app>&CB00619;吽</p>
<lb n="0527a23"/><p>又如前愛<app type="＊" source="0527002"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>。名愛結女<note n="0527005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【甲】</note><app n="0527005"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0527a24"/><p type="dharani">唵塞泥<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>抳<note place="inline">二</note><note n="0527006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）細註【甲】</note><app n="0527006"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0527a25"/><p>又以前意氣。名自在主女曰</p>
<lb n="0527a26"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>孽尾<note place="inline">一</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0527a27"/><p>又以止觀上仰如華。名春曰</p>
<lb n="0527a28"/><p type="dharani">唵末度&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>具唵<note place="inline">二合下同</note>具唵<note place="inline">二合下同</note></p>
<lb n="0527a29"/><p>又以止觀下覆如香。名夏曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0527b" n="0527b"/>
<lb n="0527b01"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>迷祇曳<note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note place="inline">入</note>吒</p>
<lb n="0527b02"/><p>又以二加眼。名秋曰</p>
<lb n="0527b03"/><p type="dharani">唵捨<note n="0527007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喇＝&CB00770;【甲】</note><app n="0527007"><lem>喇</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00770;</rdg></app>&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>惡<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0527008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＋（引）細註【甲】</note><app n="0527008"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惡<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0527b04"/><p>又以二當心。轉名冬曰</p>
<lb n="0527b05"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>勢始&CB00942;惡惡</p>
<lb n="0527b06"/><p>四攝如前依次而<note n="0527009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔用〕－【甲】</note><app n="0527009"><lem>用</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。次復以四明召尊入身
<lb n="0527b07"/>已</p>
<lb n="0527b08"/><p>復結本尊三<note n="0527010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【甲】＊</note><app n="0527010"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>耶大契。誦摩訶衍百字真言。
<lb n="0527b09"/>由是加持無上菩提尚不難得。何況諸餘成
<lb n="0527b10"/>就。設犯五無間罪。纔誦消滅無餘。何以故。由
<lb n="0527b11"/>本尊堅住己身故。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0527b12"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵三麼也麼努播&CB00256;也&CB00085;日
<lb n="0527b13"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵底<app type="＊" source="0525013"><lem>吠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB05459;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>努播底瑟&CB00062;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;哩
<lb n="0527b14"/><note place="inline">二合下同</note>荼鳥<note place="inline">二合</note>弭婆&CB00085;素&CB00418;史庾<note place="inline">二合</note>弭婆&CB00085;阿
<lb n="0527b15"/>努囉訖&CB00107;<note place="inline">二合</note>弭婆&CB00085;素補史庾<note place="inline">二合</note>弭婆&CB00085;薩
<lb n="0527b16"/>&CB00085;悉地孕<note place="inline">二合</note>弭&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>也縒薩&CB00085;羯磨素左
<lb n="0527b17"/>迷質多室&CB00942;<note place="inline">二合</note>藥矩嚕吽訶訶訶訶縠<note place="inline">引</note>婆
<lb n="0527b18"/>&CB00344;挽薩&CB00085;怛他孽多&CB00085;日邏<note place="inline">二合</note>麼冥悶左&CB00085;
<lb n="0527b19"/>日唎<note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;摩訶三摩耶薩埵惡<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0527b20"/><p>次以內外供養。供養密言<note n="0527011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【甲】</note><app n="0527011"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>。固縛禪智&CB00594;。
<lb n="0527b21"/>名戲嬉菩薩曰</p>
<lb n="0527b22"/><p type="dharani">唵<app type="＊" source="0527010"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">麼</rdg></app>訶囉底</p>
<lb n="0527b23"/><p>纔作明印。麼訶囉底女適悅契諸聖。便伸臂
<lb n="0527b24"/>向前合腕。名鬘菩薩曰</p>
<lb n="0527b25"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00080;波戌鞞</p>
<lb n="0527b26"/><p>由是印真言。持鬘女使普遍佛剎海。雨散金
<lb n="0527b27"/>剛鬘</p>
<lb n="0527b28"/><p>以印從臍至口散。名歌供養菩薩曰</p>
<lb n="0527b29"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB02122;&CB00080;<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>掃契</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0527c" n="0527c"/>
<lb n="0527c01"/><p>由是密印及真<note n="0527012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕－【甲】</note><app n="0527012"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>金剛歌女有一切世界微
<lb n="0527c02"/>塵數妓樂女。以美妙音聲。周十方剎而為供
<lb n="0527c03"/>養。<note n="0527013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝行獲【甲】</note><app n="0527013"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">行獲</rdg></app>獲如來無礙辯。便以二旋舞金剛合掌
<lb n="0527c04"/>頂上散。名舞菩薩曰</p>
<lb n="0527c05"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;布而</p>
<lb n="0527c06"/><p>由是供養獲六神通次以縛下名焚香菩薩曰</p>
<lb n="0527c07"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note n="0527014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">邏＝&CB00086;二合【甲】</note><app n="0527014"><lem>邏</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00086;二合</rdg></app>&CB00135;&CB00135;</p>
<lb n="0527c08"/><p>由是法故。得香雲遍周一切佛剎。又以上散
<lb n="0527c09"/>如華。名華菩薩曰</p>
<lb n="0527c10"/><p type="dharani">唵頗&CB00256;&CB00344;弭</p>
<lb n="0527c11"/><p>由是得華雲周遍一切佛剎。獲如來三十二
<lb n="0527c12"/>相。以禪智&CB00594;相逼金剛縛。名燈菩薩曰</p>
<lb n="0527c13"/><p type="dharani">唵蘇底惹仡哩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0527c14"/><p>由是得智光。普照佛界而為供養。獲如來五
<lb n="0527c15"/>眼。以縛當心塗香勢。名塗香菩薩曰</p>
<lb n="0527c16"/><p type="dharani">唵蘇巘蕩儗</p>
<lb n="0527c17"/><p>由是戒香普塗佛剎故。獲得五分法身智。復
<lb n="0527c18"/>以金剛合掌置於頂上。誦前虛空庫真言。出
<lb n="0527c19"/>生一切供養雲海而為供養。復往本尊羯磨
<lb n="0527c20"/>儀則。隨力念誦。次執珠合掌捧於頂上。誦本
<lb n="0527c21"/>明加持當心。一一與真言文句齊度。或萬千
<lb n="0527c22"/>百。晝夜四時精進修。念誦畢已。復以八供養
<lb n="0527c23"/>及普供養等印。供養已。復結本尊及眷屬印。
<lb n="0527c24"/>復示三麼耶。及發願等。復降三世左旋解界。
<lb n="0527c25"/>以縛印伸忍願如針。心上掣開頂上合掌。想
<lb n="0527c26"/>聖眾還本宮觀。名解脫印真言曰</p>
<lb n="0527c27"/><p type="dharani">唵訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00107;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;薩&CB00085;薩埵囉他<note place="inline">二合</note>悉地努
<lb n="0527c28"/>多也他努&CB00344;孽縒特挽<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱尾灑焰補娜
<lb n="0527c29"/><app type="＊" source="0526007"><lem>邏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app>&CB00344;麼娜也&CB00418;唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵穆</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1122.0528a" n="0528a"/>
<lb n="0528a01"/><p>作是法已。復如前加持灌頂被甲禮四如來。
<lb n="0528a02"/>發願懺悔等。身住本尊觀。無間菩提心。方出
<lb n="0528a03"/>道場。隨心轉經印塔及像隨意經行</p>
<lb n="0528a04"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>金剛頂<app type="＊" source="0526001"><lem>瑜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">踰</rdg></app>伽他化自在天理趣會普賢修行
<lb n="0528a05"/>念誦儀軌</jhead></juan></div1>
